Manage MCPAgentSession resources

Usage:
  mcp-runtime access session [command]

Available Commands:
  apply       Apply a session manifest
  delete      Delete an access session
  get         Get an access session
  list        List access sessions
  revoke      Revoke an agent session
  unrevoke    Clear the revoked flag on an agent session

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for session

Global Flags:
      --debug      Enable debug mode with structured error logging
      --use-kube   Use direct Kubernetes mode with kubectl; requires admin/operator cluster access (admin/dev/test only)

Use "mcp-runtime access session [command] --help" for more information about a command.
